7phY1UZZy2F9WYg">Thuỷ vân hương - 水雲鄉</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/H%E1%BB%93-Xu%C3%A2n-H%C6%B0%C6%A1ng/author-PBy92bBuBMMs53v9tc9E0A">Hồ Xuân Hương</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tu%E1%BB%87-Trung-th%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng-s%C4%A9/Tr%E1%BB%A5-tr%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng-t%E1%BB%AD/poem-oyMEQnV9kwW8UumMT7gdvQ">Trụ trượng tử - 柱杖子</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tu%E1%BB%87-Trung-th%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng-s%C4%A9/author-vnduJD_TYrIrUDl9fyOqRw">Tuệ Trung thượng sĩ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Duy/Y%C3%AAn-Chi-h%C3%A0nh/poem-3E00fLMXNpzWXZkyeUTVMQ">Yên Chi hành - 燕支行</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Duy/author-9f1Hth0gmM_PXzGNXg5Fog">Vương Duy</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
